videos.description: Texas Tech quarterback Nic Shimonek's pass is nearly intercepted in the end zone keeping the Red Raiders to just a field goal on their opening drive.
videos.headline: TCU defense holds Texas Tech to FG on first drive

videos.description: TCU freshman backup quarterback Shawn Robinson keeps the ball and breaks for a long run to put TCU in scoring position.
videos.headline: TCU freshman QB breaks for 41-yard run

videos.description: KaVontae Turpin runs it in from the 2-yard line to give the Horned Frogs an early lead.
videos.headline: TCU scores on short TD run from Turpin

videos.description: Justin Stockton runs to the outside and picks up a 32-yard gain to put the Red Raiders at the TCU 21-yard line.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Stockton breaks for nice run

videos.description: Nic Shimonek is sacked by Ty Summers for a loss of 11 yards forcing the Red Raiders to kick a field goal that is missed.
videos.headline: TCU defense registers sack to force FG attempt

videos.description: Justus Parker forces TCU quarterback Shawn Robinson to fumble the ball and Vaughnte Dorsey recovers it to give the Red Raiders the ball in the red zone.
videos.headline: Texas Tech defense forces fumble to stop TCU

videos.description: Shawn Robinson completes a pass to Jalen Reagor who runs into the end zone to extend TCU's lead.
videos.headline: TCU's Robinson finds Reagor for 12-yard TD

videos.description: Clayton Hatfield attempts a 20-yard field goal and shanks it way to the left.
videos.headline: Texas Tech kicker hooks field goal...by a lot!

videos.description: Nic Shimonek keeps the ball and runs it but he fumbles it as he comes to the ground. After the review, TCU is awarded the ball.
videos.headline: Texas Tech turns the ball over with fumble
